net.ttddyy.dsproxy.proxy

Interface ProxyJdbcObject


  • public interface ProxyJdbcObject
    Provide a method to unwrap the original jdbc object from proxy object.

    Proxy object created by JdbcProxyFactory implements this interface.

    Author:
    Tadaya Tsuyukubo
    See Also:
    JdbcProxyFactory, ConnectionInvocationHandler, StatementInvocationHandler, PreparedStatementInvocationHandler, CallableStatementInvocationHandler, ResultSetInvocationHandler
